WEBVTT

00:05:27.720 --> 00:05:32.040
2.5% handling fee is about 25,000 yuan.

00:05:32.040 --> 00:05:34.760
So every large purchase you make

00:05:34.760 --> 00:05:36.920
is to help them make money.

00:05:36.920 --> 00:05:40.400
And if you are an exclusive customer with a black card,

00:05:40.400 --> 00:05:42.400
you can buy anything you want. You

00:05:42.400 --> 00:05:43.840
used 1.08 billion to

00:05:43.840 --> 00:05:46.960
buy Picasso's "Woman with a Watch",

00:05:46.960 --> 00:05:49.360
and the 2.5% handling fee

00:05:49.360 --> 00:05:52.960
made the credit card company earn 27 million yuan. The

00:05:52.960 --> 00:05:55.760
second method is to use interest,

00:05:55.800 --> 00:05:57.800
targeting a group of low-income people who

00:05:57.800 --> 00:05:59.480
only pay the minimum repayment amount and

00:05:59.480 --> 00:06:02.280
maintain a long-term debt status. I
